name: Recollection of a Meal - BLUEBERRY COOKIES
description: Historical Log of Apocalyptic Events Near You is proud to enchant your visual senses with: A lovely childhood memory of times long past! These blueberry cookies, baked and filled with the purest love of a Grandmother to her Grandchildren, is sure to remind you of a much better time in the history of our species- Laid on a bed of silk as pure in it's lack of tinctures as our lost innocence, every crumb will bathe your visual tastebuds with a sea of blueberry flavor!
